UID:KNNwyWsqXVY2yskkGfm1-
SUMMARY:Woodinville Market Fair: Spring April event
DTSTAMP:20260405T040305Z
DTSTART:20260418T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Spring is in the air\, Seahawks spirit is everywhere\, and the 
	Woodinville Market Fair is bursting back to life! Join us on April 18th as
	 we kick off a brand‑new season filled with incredible local vendors\, del
	icious food trucks\, raffle prizes\, and all the warm\, welcoming energy t
	hat makes our community shine. It’s the perfect way to celebrate fresh beg
	innings and the start of another unforgettable Woodinville Market Fair sea
	son. Both of our locations are family‑friendly spaces\, perfect for spendi
	ng a spring day together and celebrating fresh beginnings.Vendors interest
	ed in participating — we’d love to have you! Send us a message for details
	 on how to join the lineup.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/detai
	ls/woodinville-market-fair-spring-april-event/18109895/2026-04-18T00\n\nFr
